General.Name: Kula Gold Ltd
General.Description: Kula Gold Limited, together with its subsidiaries, identifies and explores for metals in Western Australia. The company primarily explores for gold, lithium, halloysite, nickel, kaolin, and copper deposits, as well as platinum group elements. Kula Gold Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Perth, Australia.
